100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation"><tbody style="width:100%"><tr style="width:100%"><td data-id="__react-email-column" style="padding-top:32px"><p style="font-size:11px;line-height:14px;margin:0;font-family:&#x27;JetBrains Mono&#x27;, &#x27;SFMono-Regular&#x27;, Menlo, Consolas, &#x27;Liberation Mono&#x27;, monospace;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.64);margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Field notes</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="background:#F6F4EF;padding:40px 32px"><tbody><tr><td><img alt="Why your crew ignores your project management software" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503387762-592deb58ef4e?w=1200&amp;q=80" style="display:block;outline:none;border:0;text-decoration:none;width:100%;max-width:496px;height:auto;border-radius:2px" width="496"/><div style="height:32px;line-height:32px;font-size:1px"> </div><h1 style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:Mohave, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:28px;line-height:34px;font-weight:600;color:#0A0A0A;letter-spacing:0.02em">Why your crew ignores your project management software</h1><p style="font-size:13px;line-height:20px;margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:Mohave, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:400;color:rgba(10,10,10,0.56);margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0">Jackson<!-- -->,</p><p style="font-size:16px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:Mohave, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:400;color:rgba(10,10,10,0.84);margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0">Nobody reads a Gantt chart at 6am with coffee in their hand.</p><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-top:1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.12);margin:24px 0"/><div style="font-family:Mohave, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;color:rgba(10,10,10,0.84)"><p>The first crew I ran on Jobber quit after two weeks.</p><p>Not the software&#x27;s fault — but the friction killed them.</p></div><div style="height:32px;line-height:32px;font-size:1px"> </div><a href="https://opsapp.co/blog/preview" style="line-height:1;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;max-width:100%;mso-padding-alt:0px;background:#0A0A0A;color:#FFFFFF;padding:16px 32px;font-family:&#x27;JetBrains Mono&#x27;, &#x27;SFMono-Regular&#x27;, Menlo, Consolas, &#x27;Liberation Mono&#x27;, monospace;font-size:13px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:1.8px;text-transform:uppercase;border-radius:2px;border:1px solid #0A0A0A;padding-top:16px;padding-right:32px;padding-bottom:16px;padding-left:32px" target="_blank"><span><!--[if mso]><i style="mso-font-width:400%;mso-text-raise:24" hidden>&#8202;&#8202;&#8202;&#8202;</i><![endif]--></span><span style="max-width:100%;display:inline-block;line-height:120%;mso-padding-alt:0px;mso-text-raise:12px">Read on opsapp.co →</span><span><!--[if mso]><i style="mso-font-width:400%" hidden>&#8202;&#8202;&#8202;&#8202;&#8203;</i><![endif]--></span></a></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="background:#0A0A0A;padding:0 32px 32px"><tbody><tr><td><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-top:none;border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);margin:0 0 24px 0"/><p style="font-size:11px;line-height:14px;margin:0 0 8px 0;font-family:&#x27;JetBrains Mono&#x27;, &#x27;SFMono-Regular&#x27;, Menlo, Consolas, &#x27;Liberation Mono&#x27;, monospace;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.44);margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0">// <!-- -->OPS LTD.</p><p style="font-size:12px;line-height:18px;margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:Mohave, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.64);margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0">1515 Douglas St, Victoria, BC V8W 2G4, Canada</p><p style="font-size:12px;line-height:18px;margin:0;font-family:Mohave, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.44);margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">You&#x27;re receiving this because you subscribed to <!-- -->OPS account notifications<!-- -->.<!-- --> <a href="https://opsapp.co/unsubscribe?email=preview@example.com" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.64);text-decoration-line:none;text-decoration:underline" target="_blank">Unsubscribe</a> or <!-- -->write us at<!-- --> <a href="mailto:support@opsapp.co" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.64);text-decoration-line:none;text-decoration:underline" target="_blank">support@opsapp.co</a>.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="background:#0A0A0A;padding:16px 32px 32px"><tbody><tr><td><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation"><tbody style="width:100%"><tr style="width:100%"><td data-id="__react-email-column"><p style="font-size:12px;line-height:18px;margin:0 0 8px 0;font-family:Mohave, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.72);margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0">OPS Ltd. — Built by trades, for trades.<br/><a href="https://app.opsapp.co" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.72);text-decoration-line:none;text-decoration:none" target="_blank">app.opsapp.co</a></p><p style="font-size:11px;line-height:16px;margin:8px 0 0 0;font-family:&#x27;JetBrains Mono&#x27;, &#x27;SFMono-Regular&#x27;, Menlo, Consolas, &#x27;Liberation Mono&#x27;, monospace;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.44);margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0">Sent from <!-- -->field@opsapp.co</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></