><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation"><tbody style="width:100%"><tr style="width:100%"><td data-id="__react-email-column" style="padding-top:32px"><p style="font-size:11px;line-height:14px;margin:0;font-family:&#x27;JetBrains Mono&#x27;, &#x27;SFMono-Regular&#x27;, Menlo, Consolas, &#x27;Liberation Mono&#x27;, monospace;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.64);margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">New crew member</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="background:#F6F4EF;padding:40px 32px"><tbody><tr><td><h1 style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:Mohave, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:28px;line-height:34px;font-weight:600;color:#0A0A0A;letter-spacing:0.02em">Sam Harper<!-- -->&#x27;s in. Give them a role.</h1><p style="font-size:16px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:Mohave, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:400;color:rgba(10,10,10,0.84);margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0"><strong>Sam Harper</strong> just joined <!-- -->CanPro Deck and Rail<!-- --> on OPS. Until you assign a role, they&#x27;ll have limited access and won&#x27;t see jobs.</p><div style="height:24px;line-height:24px;font-size:1px"> </div><a href="https://app.opsapp.co/team/preview" style="line-height:1;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;max-width:100%;mso-padding-alt:0px;background:#0A0A0A;color:#FFFFFF;padding:16px 32px;font-family:&#x27;JetBrains Mono&#x27;, &#x27;SFMono-Regular&#x27;, Menlo, Consolas, &#x27;Liberation Mono&#x27;, monospace;font-size:13px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:1.8px;text-transform:uppercase;border-radius:2px;border:1px solid #0A0A0A;padding-top:16px;padding-right:32px;padding-bottom:16px;padding-left:32px" target="_blank"><span><!--[if mso]><i style="ms