      src: url(https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Mohave:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap) format('woff2');
    }

    * {
      font-family: 'Mohave', Helvetica;
    }
  </style><style>
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono';
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: 400;
      mso-font-alt: 'monospace';
      src: url(https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap) format('woff2');
    }

    * {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }
  </style></head><body style="background:#0A0A0A;margin:0;padding:0"><!--$--><!--html--><!--head--><div style="display:none;overflow:hidden;line-height:1px;opacity:0;max-height:0;max-width:0" data-skip-in-text="true">3 days left on your OPS trial<div> ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿ ‌​‍‎‏﻿</div></div><!--body--><table border="0" width="100%" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" align="center"><tbody><tr><td style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#0A0A0A;font-family:Mohave, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif"><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="max-width:560px;width:100%;margin:0 auto;padding:0"><tbody><tr style="width:100%"><td><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="background:#0A0A0A;padding:40px 32px"><tbody><tr><td><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation"><tbody style="width:100%"><tr style="width:100%"><td data-id="__react-email-column"><p style="font-size:18px;line-height:1;margin:0;font-family:Mohave, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#FFFFFF;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">OPS</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation"><tbody style="width:100%"><tr style="width:100%"><td data-id="__react-email-column" style="padding-top:32px"><p style="font-size:11px;line-height:14px;margin:0;font-family:&#x27;JetBrains Mono&#x27;, &#x27;SFMono-Regular&#x27;, Menlo, Consolas, &#x27;Liberation Mono&#x27;, monospace;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.64);margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Trial reminder</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="background:#F6F4EF;padding:40px 32px"><tbody><tr><td><h1 style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:Mohave, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:28px;line-height:34px;font-weight:600;color:#0A0A0A;letter-spacing:0.02em">3 days left on your OPS trial.</h1><p style="font-size:16px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:Mohave, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:400;color:rgba(10,10,10,0.84);margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0">Your trial ends <strong>April 18</strong>. After that, the app locks — your crew opens it the next morning and sees nothing.</p><p style="font-size:16px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:Mohave, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:400;color:rgba(10,10,10,0.84);margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0">I built OPS because every other app on the market was built by people who never swung a hammer. If you&#x27;ve made it this far, you&#x27;ve seen the difference. Your crew opens it, knows where to go, and work starts on time. That&#x27;s the whole point.</p><p style="font-size:16px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:Mohave, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:400;color:rgba(10,10,10,0.84);margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0">Don&#x27;t let your team get caught out. Lock in a plan before the trial ends.</p><div style="height:24px;line-height:24px;font-size:1px"> </div><a href="https://app.opsapp.co/settings/billing" style="line-height:1;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;max-width:100%;mso-padding-alt:0px;background:#0A0A0A;color:#FFFFFF;padding:16px 32px;font-family:&#x27;JetBrains Mono&#x27;, &#x27;SFMono-Regular&#x27;, Menlo, Consolas, &#x27;Liberation Mono&#x27;, monospace;font-size:13px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:1.8px;text-transform:uppercase;border-radius:2px;border:1px solid #0A0A0A;padding-top:16px;padding-right:32px;padding-bottom:16px;padding-left:32px" target="_blank"><span><!--[if mso]><i style="mso-font-width:400%;mso-text-raise:24" hidden>&#8202;&#8202;&#8202;&#8202;</i><![endif]--></span><span style="max-width:100%;display:inline-block;line-height:120%;mso-padding-alt:0px;mso-text-raise:12px">Pick your plan →</span><span><!--[if mso]><i style="mso-font-width:400%" hidden>&#8202;&#8202;&#8202;&#8202;&#8203;</i><![endif]--></span></a><div style="height:32px;line-height:32px;font-size:1px"> </div><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-top:1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.12);margin:16px 0"/><p style="font-size:13px;line-height:20px;margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:Mohave, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:400;color:rgba(10,10,10,0.56);margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0">— Jack<br/>Founder, OPS</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="background:#0A0A0A;padding:0 32px 32px"><tbody><tr><td><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-top:none;border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);margin:0 0 24px 0"/><p styl